---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<BaseLayout lang="en" title="Privacy Policy — Printzen">
  <Nav lang="en" />

  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-8">Last updated: July 2026</p>

      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">This Privacy Policy explains how Printzen ("we", "us") collects, uses, and protects your information when you purchase or use our software.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>At purchase (via Google Play):</strong></p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Purchases are processed entirely by Google Play. Your name, email address, and payment information are collected and handled by Google, according to Google's own Privacy Policy — we never receive or store this information.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>When you contact support:</strong></p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-1">
        <li>Your email address and the content of your message</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-1">
        <li>To respond to support inquiries you send us</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We do not collect, process, or store any purchase, license, or device information ourselves — entitlement is verified directly between the app and Google Play.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">3. Data Storage</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We do not operate a backend server for this app. No purchase, license, or device data is stored by us. Purchase records are stored and managed entirely by Google Play.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">4. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We do not sell or share personal data with third parties. Purchases are processed by Google Play according to Google's own Privacy Policy.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">5. The App — No Tracking</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">The Mobile Print Service Android application does not collect analytics, does not track usage, and does not send any data to third-party advertising services.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">6. Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We do not store personal data beyond support correspondence. You may request deletion of any support emails by contacting us. For data related to your Google Play purchase, refer to Google's own privacy controls.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">7. Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">For privacy inquiries: <a href="mailto:support@printzen.app" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">support@printzen.app</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer lang="en" />
</BaseLayout>
